### Admin Order Management with Notifications
### This file demonstrates the enhanced notification functionality for admin order management

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 1. Login as admin to get authentication token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@demo.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("admin_token", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### 2. Get all orders to find an order to update
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 3. Update order status (sends notification to user)
### Replace {orderId} with actual order ID from previous request
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders/402/status
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

"HISTORIC"

### 4. Get all order items to find an item to update
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders/items
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 5. Update individual order item status to IN_PROGRESS (sends notification)
### Replace {orderItemId} with actual order item ID from previous request
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/order-items/353/status
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

"IN_PROGRESS"

### 6. Update order item status to IN_DELIVERY (sends notification)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/order-items/353/status
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

"IN_DELIVERY"

### 7. Update order item status to DELIVERED (sends notification)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/order-items/353/status
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

"DELIVERED"

### 8. Demonstrate cancellation during IN_PROGRESS (special notification)
### First set item back to IN_PROGRESS
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/order-items/2/status
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

"IN_PROGRESS"

### 9. Cancel the order item (sends cancellation notification)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/order-items/2/status
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

"CANCELLED"

### 10. Bulk update order statuses (sends notifications to all affected users)
### This updates all PAID items for a specific delivery date to IN_PROGRESS
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders/bulk-status
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deliveryDate": "2024-12-15T00:00:00Z",
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS",
  "previousStatus": "PAID"
}

### 11. Bulk update to IN_DELIVERY (sends notifications)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders/bulk-status
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deliveryDate": "2024-12-15T00:00:00Z",
  "status": "IN_DELIVERY",
  "previousStatus": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### 12. Bulk cancel specific item (sends cancellation notifications)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders/bulk-status
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deliveryDate": "2024-12-15T00:00:00Z",
  "itemName": "Chicken Curry",
  "status": "CANCELLED",
  "previousStatus": "IN_DELIVERY"
}

### 13. Login as regular user to check notifications
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@demo.com",
  "password": "user123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("user_token", response.body.token);
%}

### 14. Check user notifications to see all the notifications sent
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### 15. Check unread notification count
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user/notifications/unread/count
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}